Text: After Vets Fight War, Feds Demand Money Back… But Illegals And Refugees Can Keep Their Money by IWB · October 27, 2016 Tweet   Thanks you for your service? No. After promising bonuses & education benefits to military in order to get them to re-enlist for the Afghanistan & Iraq Wars, the Pentagon is now demanding the money back from vets who can’t afford to pay. This is how Obama treats veterans — just like Hillary treats those who protect her in the Secret Service. Can nayone trust their promises?   Illegals And Refugees Can Keep Their Money   Military Soldiers Made To Pay Bonuses Back But Illegals And Refugees Can Keep There Money
